    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that's been super well-loved? This beauty has been my go-to for road trips and daily commutes alike, and it's still running like a total champ! It\u2019s in great shape and honestly just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. I\u2019ve kept up with the basics and it\u2019s treated me so well. Come give it a look\u2014I'd love for it to go to a great home!",
