    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the Carbon Black finish shows minor stone peppering and the interior bolsters exhibit light patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are excellent. A true enthusiast's specimen that prioritizes performance kinematics and drivetrain reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Regularly maintained. Reliable performance.",
