    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of its model year. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road-wear blemishes and light surface scratches visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free, featuring supple leather seats with minimal bolster wear and a fully functional infotainment system. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and all scheduled maintenance is documented and up-to-date. It offers a smooth, quiet ride with no unusual noises, vibrations, or leaks. This is a reliable, well-cared-for car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any looming repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
