      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks awesome on the road? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, super clean, and it runs like a total dream. Whether you're heading out for a weekend getaway or just cruising around town, this beauty is ready for its next big adventure with you. You're going to love how it handles. Come check it out!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
