      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, providing a linear torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with a MacPherson front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. This is a driver-oriented machine with crisp throttle response and a balanced polar moment of inertia, ready for the purist who values mechanical transparency.",
